column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.subclass,s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.veldisp, p.lnLDeV_g FROM PhotoObjall AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.class = &&& and s.veldisperr > # and s.veldisp > #*s.veldisperr and   p.petroR5#err_u > # and p.petroR5#_u > #*p.petroR5#err_u and   p.petroR5#err_g > # and p.petroR5#_g > #*p.petroR5#err_g and  p.petroR5#err_r > # and p.petroR5#_r > #*p.petroR5#err_r and  p.petroR5#err_i > # and p.petroR5#_i > #*p.petroR5#err_i and  p.petroR5#err_z > # and p.petroR5#_z > #*p.petroR5#err_z
